# RunPod GPU jobs: GitHub Actions only

Never launch RunPod training from a local Mac or Cursor agent shell (`tools/runpod_train.py --yes`,
`runpod-sft-3seed.sh`, `runpod-dpo-3seed.sh`, etc.). Outbound SSH to RunPod mapped pod
high-ports times out from local Cursor egress.

Use GitHub Actions instead:

- **sophia-7b SFT/DPO:** `.github/workflows/runpod-sophia-7b-sft.yml`
- **Generic LoRA train:** `.github/workflows/train-runpod.yml`
- **Speedup bench:** `.github/workflows/speedup-runpod.yml`
- **RLVR:** `.github/workflows/rlvr-runpod.yml`

Requires repo secret `RUNPOD_API_KEY`. Trigger via Actions → workflow → Run workflow (confirm=`RUN`).

Evidence: `agi-proof/sophia-7b-train-verify/stage2-runpod-blocker.public-report.json`.
